Package es.gva.cit.gazetteer.querys

Class Summary
Feature This class represents a Feature into the WFS context
FeatureType This class represents a thesaurus name (city, cementer, ...)
FeatureTypeAttribute This class represents a field from a thesaurus name (name,description,...)
GazetteerOptions This class is used to manage the aspect and the filter of the gazetteer.
GazetteerQuery This class contains all the queryable fields that the user interface supports.
